## TransferPanel
:::demo
```html
<mtd-transfer-panel
  :data="initData"
  :defaultChecked="[]"
  title="未选"
  filterable
>
</mtd-transfer-panel>
<script>
  export default {
    data() {
      return {
        checkedData: [],
        operations: ['handle1', 'handle2'],
        initData: [
          {
            label: 'item-1',
            key: 1,
            disabled: false
          },
          {
            label: 'item-2',
            key: 2,
            disabled: true
          },
          {
            label: 'item-3',
            key: 3,
            disabled: false
          },
        ]
      }
    }
  }
</script>
```
